snippet.title: Spelunky 2 - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Meet the next generation of treasure hunters in Spelunky 2! Follow Ana Spelunky and her friends on an exciting new adventure as they journey deeper than they could have ever imagined... Coming to PS4 and Steam in 2019!

Trailer by: Derek Lieu

http://www.twitter.com/derek_lieu
https://www.derek-lieu.com/

Derek Yu: http://www.twitter.com/mossmouth
BlitWorks: http://www.twitter.com/blitworks
Eirik Suhrke: http://www.twitter.com/strotchy

http://www.spelunkyworld.com
